<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--
    Music Catalog - Public Read-Only Interface
    
    This is the public-facing version of the Music Catalog.
    DO NOT sync authentication or CRUD features from index.html.
    
    Public features only:
    - View catalog (read-only)
    - Search and filter
    - Sort columns
    - View statistics
    - Auto-refresh
    
    Private features (NOT included):
    - Login/logout
    - Add/edit/delete albums
    - Authentication
    - Admin controls
-->
<html lang="en">
<head>
